<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.3.10">
<l>kārikai yārkku muṉakku miḻukkuṟṟeṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">kātukaḷ vīṅki yeriyil</l>
<l>tāriyā tākil talainon tiṭumeṉṟu</l>
<l rend="indent">viṭṭiṭṭēṉ kuṟṟamē yaṉṟē</l>
<l>cēriyiṟ piḷḷaika ḷellāruṅ kātu</l>
<l rend="indent">perukkit tiriyavuṅ kāṇṭi</l>
<l>yērviṭai ceṟṟiḷaṅ kaṉṟeṟin tiṭṭa</l>
<l rend="indent">viruṭīkē cāveṉṟaṉ kaṇṇē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What harm is it to you and these women if my ears swell and burn?</l>
<l>Is it not distressing to me who, when it became intolerable,</l>
<l>gave up, thinking “[it] hurts [his] head”?</l>
<l>Won’t you look as all the boys in the village wander [about],</l>
<l rend="indent">having had their ears expanded.</l>
<l>O Hṛṣīkēśa who, having overcome the ploughing bull,</l>
<l rend="indent">threw the young calf, O my Eye!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
